snippet.title: Cult of the Frog | A Cozy Walking Sim With Puzzles
snippet.description:
Cult of the frog is a relaxing, cozy walking simulator. Embark on an enchanting journey as a frog archaeologist on a mystical island full of secrets. Find the ancient ruins of the enigmatic Cult of the Frog, uncovering long-lost relics and untold stories.
